<section class="section" id="yourjam">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div>
        <h2>If This Sounds Like Your Jam, You're in the Right Place</h2>
        <p>Feel like the weeks are blurring together?<br />Is life moving too fast?</p>
        <p>Getting tired of the same routine?</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>If yes, Maceda is exactly what you need:</li>
          <li>Days shaped by tides (not work calls or screens)</li>
          <li>Real surf fundamentals taught by skilled coaches</li>
          <li>Intermediate to advanced progression pathways</li>
          <li>33 years of proven surf instructing experience</li>
          <li>Intimate gatherings and live music (but never chaos)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#book" class="btn">Book Now!</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/fun.webp" alt="Fun at Maceda Surf Camp" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .checklist {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .checklist li {
    padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .checklist li::before {
    content: '•';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .checklist li:first-child::before {
    content: '';
  }

  .checklist li:first-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
</style>
